flowchart LR
  Draft["Draft answer, plan, or action"] --> Criteria["Quality criteria and constraints"]
  Criteria --> Critique["Reflect: find concrete defects"]
  Critique --> Decision{"Actionable issue?"}
  Decision -->|"No"| Accept["Accept current result"]
  Decision -->|"Yes"| Revise["Revise output or state"]
  Revise --> Validate{"Meets criteria?"}
  Validate -->|"No, within budget"| Critique
  Validate -->|"No, budget or risk hit"| Escalate["Escalate, refuse, or stop"]
  Validate -->|"Yes"| Accept
  Accept --> Audit["Trace critique, revision, stop reason"]
  Escalate --> Audit
